# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only needed files
**

# Re-include Go source files (but not *_test.go)
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module files
!go.mod
!go.sum

# Re-include the embedded broker dashboard asset. dashboard.go has
# //go:embed dashboard_assets/index.html, so the build context MUST carry it
# or `go build` fails with "pattern ...: no matching files found".
!internal/broker/api/dashboard_assets/index.html

# Re-include the embedded agent config-console assets. server.go embeds the two
# role HTML pages and workload.go embeds the burst-workload manifest, so the
# build context MUST carry them or the agent `go build` fails the same way.
!internal/agent/console/assets/consumer.html
!internal/agent/console/assets/provider.html
!internal/agent/console/assets/burst-workload.yaml

# Re-include the host-prefetched liqoctl binary the Makefile drops under
# bin/liqoctl-<version>-<os>-<arch>/liqoctl. The agent runtime stage COPYs
# from this path instead of curling github.com during the build.
!bin/liqoctl-*/liqoctl
